The flurry part works with charmed pets, from what I have heard.  The reason it doesn't work properly with summoned pets has to do with the delay caps on pets.  A pet cannot be hasted past its minimum delay, so the extra attacks that flurry would give are ignored. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=magnasab>MagnasAB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#333333>(2/25/03 3:13:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=543.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Frenzied BO</span><hr size=1> One thing about FB on Charmed pets after the FB fades they do keep flurries and rampage.  But you do need to re B5 them as the haste does fade after the timmer is up.  You can actuly see this by watching the pet swing. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30>Magician Skills</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
